<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.195534>
    bibo:endPage "60" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "52" ;
    bibo:volume "2487" ;
    dc:creator "Fritzén, Niclas R." ;
    dc:date "2010" ;
    dc:title "Natural history and description of Zatypota kerstinae sp. nov. (Hymenoptera: Ichneumonidae) reared from Theridion palmgreni Marusik et Tsellarius (Araneae: Theridiidae) in Finland" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.195536>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.195537> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.195536>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Theridion palmgreni with (a) an overwintering larva (12. II. 2005) of a paratype male of Zatypota kerstinae sp. nov. and (b) the larva of the holotype female of Zatypota kerstinae sp. nov. three days before killing its host." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/195536/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.195537>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Zatypota kerstinae sp. nov. cocoon. The cocoon is built vertically with its anterior apex attached to some threads in the host's web. It is characterised by erect tufts at its basal end." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/195537/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

